00:09:27.140 --> 00:09:33.470
Let me just start by saying I've
been a longtime reader of history.

00:09:33.470 --> 00:09:34.770
I love history.

00:09:34.770 --> 00:09:38.990
And this came about because of my
grandfather who at the ripe old age

00:09:38.990 --> 00:09:44.860
of 15 arrived alone from
Lebanon, trying to find his sister

00:09:44.860 --> 00:09:47.800
