American Senate, the House of Lords,

00:24:25.770 --> 00:24:30.630
the World Federation of Twin Towns
followed and all unanimously agreed

00:24:30.630 --> 00:24:34.390
to declare Tyre a world
heritage site.

00:24:34.390 --> 00:24:37.500
