01:00:16.510 --> 01:00:46.040
[ Speaking French ]

01:00:46.040 --> 01:00:51.080
&gt;&gt; So the first phase that actually
has been proven archaeologically

01:00:51.080 --> 01:00:52.380
to exist goes back

01:00:52.380 --> 01:00:57.190
to the Chalcolithic period
which is around 4000 BC.

01:00:57.190 --> 01:01:00.990
And the Lebanese University
was given

01:01:00.990 --> 01:01:11.510
in the '70's an archaeological
find that dates to that period.

01:01:11.510 --> 01:01:24.540
[ Speaking French ]

01:01:24.540 --> 01:01:32.540
&gt;&gt; So a site known as [French name]
