01:12:41.510 --> 01:13:17.040
[ Speaking French ]

01:13:17.040 --> 01:13:20.080
&gt;&gt; And so we continue
all the way 700 years

01:13:20.080 --> 01:13:24.090
in time towards the 20th
century and we would

01:13:24.090 --> 01:13:27.610
like to mention Earnest
Renol in the 1860's

01:13:27.610 --> 01:13:34.420
who described the city has having
had a very prosperous past,

01:13:34.420 --> 01:13:42.510
but for some reason it has
completely fallen into decay.

01:13:42.510 --> 01:14:02.080
[ Speaking French ]

01:14:02.080 --> 01:14:07.710
&gt;&gt; And so in the -- could
