01:51:58.410 --> 01:52:04.660
And the pieces discovered are now
in the National Museum in Beirut.

01:52:04.660 --> 01:52:08.430
Since the end of the French
mandate, the collection

01:52:08.430 --> 01:52:13.510
in the Louvre was completed
by a few purchases.

01:52:13.510 --> 01:52:18.040
[ Inaudible ]

01:52:18.040 --> 01:52:20.950
Which is said to have been
found on the seashore at Sour,

01:52:20.950 --> 01:52:26.400
