dedication to [inaudible] in Tyre.

01:52:26.400 --> 01:52:32.440
A marbles stone with a full line
dedication to [inaudible] also.

01:52:32.440 --> 01:52:39.330
And [inaudible] statuettes from a
deposit at the bottom of the sea.

01:52:39.330 --> 01:52:43.730
To conclude this brief
overview we can see

01:52:43.730 --> 01:52:45.540
that in the Phoenician collection

01:52:45.540 --> 01:52:52.400
