03:17:56.510 --> 03:18:16.040
[ Speaking French ]

03:18:16.040 --> 03:18:25.080
&gt;&gt; So we witness the kidnapping
of a Tyrian princess called Europa

03:18:25.080 --> 03:18:35.510
