03:19:11.600 --> 03:19:16.360 position:56%
But it is a symbol for the joining,
for the connection between the east,

03:19:16.360 --> 03:19:22.290
Europa, the Tyrian princess,
and Zeus representing Greece.

03:19:22.290 --> 03:19:25.510
So the joining between
east and west.

03:19:25.510 --> 03:19:55.030
[ Speaking French ]

03:19:55.030 --> 03:20:04.310
&gt;&gt; So the kidnapping of Europa
towards Greece led to a myth

03:20:04.310 --> 03:20:11.200
