this beautiful princess.

03:20:11.200 --> 03:20:19.150 position:56%
And so it represents this connection
and it is of high importance

03:20:19.150 --> 03:20:25.510
to all the upcoming historians.

03:20:25.510 --> 03:20:38.530
[ Speaking French ]

03:20:38.530 --> 03:20:45.850
&gt;&gt; So Agenor the king
