03:21:45.170 --> 03:21:48.970
of the sun from the east
and towards the west.

03:21:48.970 --> 03:21:55.510
The sunset is very
symbolic of this story.

03:21:55.510 --> 03:22:29.090
[ Speaking French ]

03:22:29.090 --> 03:22:31.670
&gt;&gt; So this myth, this
legend became the subject

03:22:31.670 --> 03:22:39.860 position:56%
