periods until the 20th century.

03:22:51.510 --> 03:22:57.540
[ Speaking French ]

03:22:57.540 --> 03:23:03.600
&gt;&gt; So Herodotus in the 5th century
introduced Cadmous to his readers

03:23:03.600 --> 03:23:09.510
because he brought the
alphabet to the Greeks.

03:23:09.510 --> 03:23:45.550
[ Speaking French ]

03:23:45.550 --> 03:23:50.220
&gt;&gt; So the fact that Cadmous left
Phoenicia and went to Greece

03:23:50.220 --> 03:23:53.600
on his own and was away
from his fatherland

03:23:53.600 --> 03:23:59.980
for a very long time meant that
he adopted a different mentality.

03:23:59.980 --> 03:24:04.590 position:56%
That he became an individual and the
fact that he is a unique individual

03:24:04.590 --> 03:24:08.260
and that he created a whole process

03:24:08.260 --> 03:24:11.810
by introducing the language
is something extraordinary.

03:24:11.810 --> 03:24:19.510
And there is no country without
the effect of one individual.

03:24:19.510 --> 03:26:03.040
[ Speaking French ]

