03:27:26.510 --> 03:28:07.120
[ Speaking French ]

03:28:07.120 --> 03:28:11.400
&gt;&gt; So basically they not only
travelled the Middle Eastern coast.

03:28:11.400 --> 03:28:16.960
They also travelled towards Spain,
towards Cadiz and towards Carthage.

03:28:16.960 --> 03:28:24.510
And they dispersed the
