balanced than his own.

03:32:38.510 --> 03:33:08.310
[ Speaking French ]

03:33:08.310 --> 03:33:12.210
&gt;&gt; So what we find in Carthage is
not only a Phoenician tradition

03:33:12.210 --> 03:33:17.670
