straight to the biblical land

03:40:00.660 --> 03:40:04.750
of Kabul, present day Galilea.

03:40:04.750 --> 03:40:13.220
And where 20 settlements were later
granted by Solomon to Hiram of Tyre

03:40:13.220 --> 03:40:19.440
